data.description: Own your little piece of mountain paradise! This one of a kind log built home has everything. From the large living area to the generous kitchen. You have both formal and regular dining areas. Wood and propane heat, large newly renovated master bedroom with walk in closets and full-bath. Whether you want to live in it full time or use it as a holiday get away, you can enjoy all the wild life on either one of your covered decks. Home borders public lands, just walk or ride out to enjoy nature.
